snippet.title: RollerCoaster Tycoon Adventures (Nintendo Switch) Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the final pre-launch look at the Nintendo Switch version of RollerCoaster Tycoon, out in Europe on November 29 and in North America shortly thereafter.

Watch more trailers here!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wB8Ipb4-YHg&index=2&list=PLraFbwCoisJA6xInpo8WhMSrR3Y7CjatL&t=0s
